# Test your FastAPI endpoints

### Root endpoint
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/
Accept: application/json

###

### Get all items
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items
Accept: application/json

###

### Get single item
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/items/1
Accept: application/json

