### Test 1: Create order with single item
POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "phone_num": "555-1234",
  "user_id": 1,
  "items": [
    {
      "item_id": 1,
      "quantity": 2
    }
  ]
}

